description:
Corey auditioned with me a while back. I actually met this adorable muscle stud through his friend, Troy.

The thing about Corey is he has beautiful blue bedroom eyes, a great smile, a nice personality, and big (and I do mean BIG) muscular arms. In case you haven't guessed by now, I'm a big muscle fan, so Corey is really my kind of guy.
title: Corey
